OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering lodger and
OL,4,Cscattering body parts
OL,6,FThe victim had been living in a tent
OL,7,Fin the garden of the flat Atkins
OL,8,Fshared with his girlfriend, 39-year-
OL,9,Fold Debbie Pereira, giving the
OL,10,Fdefendants drugs in lieu of paying
OL,11,Frent.
OL,13,FThe Judge, Mrs Justice Stacey, said
OL,14,FAtkins may have initially been acting
OL,15,Fin self-defence when a fight broke out
OL,16,Fon the night of the killing, but said
OL,17,Fthe level of violence inflicted upon
OL,18,Fhim was "extreme".
