OL,4,Cscattering body parts
OL,6,FPereira was acquitted of murder but
OL,7,Fconvicted of perverting the course of
OL,8,Fjustice.
OL,10,FShe was jailed for four years after
OL,11,Fthe court heard she "hid" in her
OL,12,Fbedroom while Atkins carried out the
OL,13,Fbrutal attack but helped clean up
OL,14,Fafterwards.
OL,16,FAtkins had previously admitted
OL,17,Fperverting the course of justice and
OL,18,Fboth defendants had admitted
OL,19,Fpreventing the burial of a corpse.
